<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  front-text">
<div class="wpb_wrapper">
<p><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/U0Daqg3aimw" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p>In the latest episode of <em>Above The Fray</em>, FAS President <a href="https://fas.org/expert/ali-nouri" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ali Nouri</a>&#8216;s video podcast, he and the <a href="https://fas.org/ncov/">Coronavirus Project</a> team discuss how the important role of scientists during pandemics and how we can all pitch in to make the world safer.</p>
<p><span class="_5mfr _47e3">Past episodes are available on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCNNc5LYwPTP-HcxujseuOJQ/videos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube</a>.</span></p>
